Kaduna &mdash; The Chief of Defence Staff (CDS), General Abayomi Olanisakin, has commissioned a 1,000 seat capacity auditorium at the Air Force Institute of Technology (AFIT), Kaduna.Speaking at the commissioning, the CDS said the auditorium and the lecture hall would provide conducive environment for learning and impact on operations carried out by the Nigeria Air Force.The Chief of Air Staff, Air Marshall Sadiq Abubakar, said, earlier, that the auditorium and hall had been equipped with modern facilities and audio visual materials for effective learning.